      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(Card other)
        Compares to another card. If the calling Card is 'stronger' than the given card, the result is a positive integer, otherwise negative. If they're equally 'strong', 0 is returned. The card strength corresponds to the strength of the symbol.
        Specified by:
